<article id="post-429" class="post-429 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-uncategorised tag-athletics tag-sports">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://localhost/Chaibasa.org/2019/07/district-athletic-championship" rel="bookmark">District Athletic Championship</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<a class="post-thumbnail" href="http://localhost/Chaibasa.org/2019/07/district-athletic-championship" aria-hidden="true">
		<img width="1078" height="799" src="http://localhost/Chaibasa.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Zila-School.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="District Athletic Championship" loading="lazy" srcset="http://localhost/Chaibasa.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Zila-School.jpg 1078w, http://localhost/Chaibasa.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Zila-School-300x222.jpg 300w, http://localhost/Chaibasa.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Zila-School-768x569.jpg 768w, http://localhost/Chaibasa.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Zila-School-1024x759.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 60vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" />	</a>

		
	<div class="entry-content">
		
<p>On the 27th and 28th of July, the West Singhbhum District Athletics Championship will be held in Zila School Ground. General secretary of West Singhbhum District Athletics Association Ajay Kumar Nayak told that participants from different age groups can participate in this competition. </p>



<p>Participants can participate in various categories of under-12 boys and girls, under 14 boys and girls, under 16 boys and girls, under 18 boys and girls, under 20 boys and girls and men and women&#8217;s events. In this competition, there will be events of 100m, 200m, 400m, 800m, 1500m race, long jumping, disk throws, etc. Interested Participants can contact the Association&#8217;s office for name registration in the event.</p>



